{"tid":1059230,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"創業撚 - 信自己定信老母","createTime":"2019-03-13T04:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T12:23:44.000Z","uid":138588,"like":80,"dislike":222,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"8b21853ad1ed46ab382a17b7e194ca901e69542f","tid":1059230,"uid":138588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n先講少少背景 小弟行年三十 ive仔兼公屋仔 做咗七年野 年薪6x萬 叫做唔錯 但foreseen到前途有限 <br />\n呢排咗好耐想辭職出黎自己闖一番事業 <br />\n諗住做貿易 同本身份工冇相關<br />\n我就隨口問下老母話想辭職出黎搞生意<br />\n佢問我同邊個一齊 我話自己<br />\n佢就話叫我邊工邊做先 起碼有起色先辭職 <br />\n因為辭咗就冇收入 每月冇幾皮 同埋前路唔知係點<br />\n但我自己就認為在職做好多限制 因為平日返工做唔到咩 只可以收工做 我依家都係係收工後做research嘅階段階段 <br />\nplan緊好唔好下半年辭<br />\n<br />\n求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n信自己 - <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n信老母 - <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56787e629ea4e3fa05cc87c29df4ed23625483c","tid":1059230,"uid":196924,"like":64,"dislike":5,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"難聽啲講句<br />\n你30，你老母照計都50+<br />\n以你老母後生嗰陣嘅環境，佢思維係掂嘅一早揸住層私樓啦"},{"pid":"bc6b4fc443dc1bb4a9de732b7754b22c29c2da33","tid":1059230,"uid":838,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"信自己<br />\n除非你老母係好搵到錢嘅人"},{"pid":"dbe78f73633770fd224875e92a493279ae1fe0a6","tid":1059230,"uid":138588,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:03:55.000Z","msg":"一次回哂上面兩個一樣問題 其實係單親 住得公屋 住係窮撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e643aeb0e3f26479341d35fdbc4e83e784f86de","tid":1059230,"uid":50253,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"想跟樓主搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9c2697271e6b4bad53d9bd135b2036c7805aae","tid":1059230,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":