sg":"有冇興趣傾下合作做？<br />\n<br />\n合作又好<br />\n當識個朋友都得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"可以傾下呀 你想做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0c5aaf4a63d754252203b0479cae6d9a3a628d","tid":1059230,"uid":238424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"有月薪50k怕搵唔番工咩..出黎做一兩年都唔怕啦<br />\n加上你月薪50k.點都有儲到D錢掛"},{"pid":"ce9b83acf243505c089cad00838423ab0d3f3964","tid":1059230,"uid":29212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"講真, 你本來月入幾皮, 創業機會成本一定大, 如果唔撈之後又搞唔起你壇野, 壓力一定大, 有無諗過當副業搞住先, 撈得起先QUIT?"},{"pid":"f7bc7b6b365ab07fcf8fdad5b079c41fb8f04bef","tid":1059230,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"財政儲備夠唔夠你食一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d9b1fcc034483b1e238b58f686d743f2b52be1","tid":1059230,"uid":214380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"出來創業不是太易,你去開到個公司戶口先諗其他啦;好多本錢就唔同!"},{"pid":"de36fdbe6aa7da2ba59a827036b5e4b4d76ed6cb","tid":1059230,"uid":138588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce9b83acf243505c089cad00838423ab0d3f3964","tid":1059230,"uid":29212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"講真, 你本來月入幾皮, 創業機會成本一定大, 如果唔撈之後又搞唔起你壇野, 壓力一定大, 有無諗過當副業搞住先, 撈得起先QUIT?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"大多數意見都係叫我當副業搞住先 辛苦啲捱下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a0aac698bb728337ce752b0e33824560d49881","tid":1059230,"uid":197783,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"我係裸辭創業，2月開始到而家， 夠生活既。比起打工果陣當然少一截。<br />\n不過唔好計錢多錢少，見到由零開始，到夠三餐加生意有增長，個過程係打工俾唔到你。<br />\n<br />\n如果對自己壇野有信心，應該放手一搏。"},{"pid":"c7e114db9725f9f3a601ad35d592a8f3337e2d28","tid":1059230,"uid":44513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"為錢的話買樓好過"},{"pid":"19f3e1a97af55e1b91a73cfb9ad9f5dfa6cba195","tid":1059230,"uid":23536,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"人生得一次 你諗你 人人都會叫你唔好辭職 因為佢地活緊係comfort zone"},{"pid":"f344305e5cf73ad50c09666ee01b484a267180f1","tid":1059230,"uid":198317,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"信自己 <br />\n老母係窮人環境生活 <br />\n點會識呢d 佢點都覺得安穩最緊要<br />\n但唔搏就永遠冇機會變有錢<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"632c640bcb27030cc3595746175bedbbf0f4aa8e","tid":1059230,"uid":170133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"出錢請我幫你搞，你繼續專心扮工出糧。"},{"pid":"f2f832fe597edf581d50014ac6c05bab09a7c8a4","tid":1059230,"uid":23536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"創業本身已經好難 如果仲要係副業咁做 唔方會做得好 咁不如唔好浪費時間 <br />\n<br />\n偉大創業家十之八九都係迫出黎 絕對唔係副業發展到"},{"pid":"778bc6b09ac0cc8c29d5d1efbd7ed6ccb16e4c05","tid":1059230,"uid":55422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"師兄可以交流下喎 <br />\n利申: 都係公屋撚"},{"pid":"0b05cb0efbfbecf3608a75b6f7c7a983ebd501bc","tid":1059230,"uid":168356,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:30:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03f3920dea687fb05732b577297451ee459cbb0c","tid":1059230,"uid":59830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e41b5e26e497429c6b32177e2e7b9ed2a4bd3922","tid":1059230,"uid":138588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"多謝大家意見 前期工作好多同都相對嘥時間 例如公司註冊 開戶等等<br />\n所以我會搞掂哂先 btw好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df977d6f8695888e11f1606909d8e074ceb4f41e","tid":1059230,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"你老母有道理，辛苦少少但穩定性高好多<br />\n創得業都唔會怕辛苦架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\